      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOVA'S FERN (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (35.60) at this track behind Enhance in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Top chance in this line up. OREGON JANET (7) was below best last time when fourth at this track but prior to that among the placings in quick time (40.01) at Murray Bridge. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Well placed here and can atone this time. ZENVO YOYO (5) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (36.19) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Expected to be in this for a long way. NITRO NEO (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
